
<header class="welcome-header">
  <div class="home-vid">
    <div id="video">
      <video preload="preload" id="video" autoplay="autoplay" loop="loop">
        <source src="<%= asset_path "Toronto2.mp4" %>" type="video/mp4"></source>
      </video>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="home-title-button">
    <h1 class="welcome-title animated fadeInDown">THE SHARED ECONOMY OF GARBAGE.</h1>
    <h3 class="welcome-subtitle animated fadeInUp">Buy & sell extra garbage space in a few clicks.</h3>
    <a style="text-align:center;" href="#newuser" class="btn-front animated fadeIn">GET STARTED!</a>
    <a class="downward-scroll"><%= image_tag 'downward-arrow.png', class:"downward-arrow" %></a>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="welcome-content">
  <div class="divider"> </div>
  <div class="introduction animated fadeIn">
    <%= image_tag 'money-bags.png', :width => 100, :height => 95, class:"garbage-bag" %>
    <p class="intro-line">
      We have saved buyers <strong id="moneySaved">$<%= @sum %></strong> since launch!
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sell-container">
      <div class="when-you-sell animated">
          <h2 class="when-you-title">When you sell!</h2>
          <%= image_tag 'money-bag.png',:width => 100, :height => 95, class:"money-bag", href:"money-bag"%>
        <ul class="when-you-sell-list">
          <li>
            If you've got extra space in your garbage, you can make money!
          </li>
          <br />
          <li>
            When you sell your garbage space, you and your fellow neighbours will both
            benifit! You're helping them save money, all the while you're making money!
            The less garbage you have come garbage day, could mean more money in your pocket!
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

     <div class="buy-container">
      <div class="when-you-buy animated">
        <h2 class="when-you-title">When you buy!</h2>
        <%= image_tag 'trash-bin-full.png',:width => 100, :height => 95, class:"trash-bin-full", href:"trash-bin-full"%>
        <ul class="when-you-buy-list">
          <li>
            See if your neighbours have extra space in their garbage and save money!
          </li>
          <br />
          <li >
            When you buy garbage space, you and your fellow neighbours will both
            benifit! Don't go out and buy extra bags! Save money by checking to see
            if your neighbours have extra garbage space. If so, buy it from them and save the hassle and money!
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div> <!-- containter -->

  <div class="divider-bottom"> </div>
  <div class="intro-form">
    <div class="intro-form-container">
      <div class="signup-container animated">
        <div id="newuser">
          <%= render 'users/form' %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="login-container animated">
        <div id="login">
          <%= render 'sessions/form' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
